Uses of Package
xorgame

  • Classes in xorgame used by xorgame 
    Class and Description
    Building
    This enum contains names of buildings available in XorGame.
    BuildingOrder
    Database entity class for building_order table - containing information about buildings currently built on the planets.
    EconomyRanking
    Entity class for economy_ranking view - contains all users ordered descending by its economy points.
    Fleet
    The class represents a fleet and contains number of different kinds of ships thatthe fleet contains.
    Flight
    Entity class for flight table - contains information about moving fleets
    GameGui
    This class contains all images and texts used as a GUI in XorGame client.
    Gui
    Entity class for gui table - contains GUI images that should be displayed by the game client.
    Locale
    Entity class for locale table - contains all game client text in different languages.
    Location
    Enumeration contains possible locations at specified coordinates (planet, moon or debris).
    Material
    This enum represents possible kinds of materials in XorGame - metal, cristal, deuter, antimatter, or energy.
    Message
    Entity class for message table - message sent to another user.
    MilitaryRanking
    Entity class for military_ranking view - contains all users ordered descending by their military points.
    Mission
    Enumeration contains possible missions that a fleet can accept.
    Moon
    Entity class for moon table - represents a moon of planet in a game galaxy.
    MoonGui
    Entity class for moon_gui table - possible images of moons to display in the game client.
    MoonPK
    Entity class for primary key of a moon table.
    Planet
    Entity class for planet table - represents planet in the game galaxy.
    PlanetGui
    Entity class for planet_gui table - contains possible images of planets to display in game client.
    PlanetPK
    Entity class for primary key of planet table.
    Research
    This enum contains names of all technologies available in XorGame.
    ResearchOrder
    Entity class for research_order table - containing information about currently researched technologies.
    ResearchRanking
    Entity class for research_ranking view - containing all user ordered descending by their research points.
    ShipyardItem
    This enum contains names of all items (ships or defense systems) that can be build in the shipyard.
    ShipyardOrder
    Entity class for shipyard_order table - containing information about currently build ships and defense systems.
    SpeedRateOutOfRange
    Exception class thrown if speed rate of the fleet given as parameter to function is out of range 0.0 to 1.0 .
    Star
    Entity class for star table - representing a star in game galaxy.
    StarGui
    Entity class for star_gui table - containing possible images of stars to display in game client.
    StarPK
    Entity class for primary key of star table - containing its (X,Y) cartesian coordinates in the game galaxy.
    TotalRanking
    Entity class for total_ranking view - containing all users ordered descending by their total points.
    User
    Entity class for user table - containing all essential information about user of the game.
